# Defense-in-depth weight-file guard for the docker/ subtree.
#
# The root .gitignore on main already blocks these patterns globally
# (added in commit 34ef2e2). This nested file travels with the docker/
# subtree to the `docker` branch, so pushes directly to that branch
# are also protected. See memory project_north_star.md and the
# runtime-download plan for rationale.

*.safetensors
*.gguf
*.ckpt
*.pth
*.pt
*.onnx
*.bin
.cache/
huggingface/
models/

# Allow the pinned manifest itself through — it's just JSON.
!models.lock.json
